config BR2_PACKAGE_OPEN_TX_ISP
	bool "Open TX-ISP driver"
	depends on BR2_PACKAGE_INGENIC_SDK
	help
	  Open-source replacement for the proprietary Ingenic TX-ISP
	  firmware blob. Provides a fully open tx-isp-t31.ko driver
	  with no binary dependencies.

	  The driver supports T31 family SoCs and is compatible with
	  kernel 3.10 through 7.0.

	  From https://github.com/opensensor/open-tx-isp

	  When enabled, this replaces the blob ISP module from ingenic-sdk.

	  If unsure, say N.
